data.description: Check out this unique, completely custom-built home in popular Pacific Heights.  With only 2 owners since new in 1966, this home is perched on a large corner lot with awesome curb appeal.   No cookie-cutter here!  This spacious home includes 4 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, plus two large bonus rooms for storage, home office, workout room, etc.  Recent updates include new LVP flooring in the living room, dining room, upstairs bathrooms and the finished basement.  Fresh interior paint in many rooms.  Granite counters in the kitchen and an original wet bar in the basement.  New garage door and privacy fence.  HVAC was replaced in 2020, and roof is newer.   Located in a terrific established neighborhood in the Millard school district, this home is close to many amenities and has great access to restaurants and shops.  This home is ready for a new owner to enjoy the awesome mid-century vibe and quiet neighborhood!
